            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "It's true that this won't work for `extends` and `import`, but that is simply because jinja has no notion of requests itself. If you can think of a solution for that I will gladly implement it.\n\nAs for the problem of incorrectly expecting blueprints to take priority. This is probably mostly caused by the fact that there is a `url_prefix`, but no `template_prefix` and thus it is assumed that `template_folder` fulfills that function. So maybe `template_prefix` should be added instead.\n"
        },
